- Update to version 3.4.4:
  * Version sync with python-fastmcp-slim, which carries the
    functional changes of this release: the strict Host/Origin
    guard defaults added in 3.4.3 are relaxed to restore
    compatibility with ASGI, serverless and reverse-proxy
    deployments (the guard stays available for opt-in trusted
    hosts and origins), plus a new Hugging Face OAuth provider

